# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# belief-recipes.form — the frequency bank: how each belief system
# meets the moment shit happens, as configurations of one engine
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The satsang at Llena's (Ubud, 2026-05-07) drew its topic "from major
# physiology, science, and religions in their most core words: what do
# we do when shit happens." Two layers came out of that room:
#
#   · the five strategies of return that circle members had each found
#     — recorded in when-the-pressure-comes.form and
#     lc-when-the-pressure-comes
#   · the survey itself: every philosophy and belief system carries its
#     own complete recipe for failure, pain, the recognition of a 'bad'
#     event — the same arrival, met through different teachings
#
# The second layer arrived into the body 2026-06-11, named by Urs as
# lineage clarification (the session's transmission record is honest
# absence). This file and `form/form-stdlib/belief-recipes.fk` carry
# it: the operator's FREQUENCY dial — "which belief system carries
# this" — opened into a runnable bank. SHIPPED:
# `tests/belief-recipes-band.fk` → 255, three-way (Go/Rust/TS).
#
# The structural claim, proven: the SAME bad event (the body's shape,
# the probe, what the world delivered) meets eight attested teachings,
# and each lands a distinct, exact, falsifiable signature — yet every
# one is a configuration of the one metabolic engine. Traditions are
# DATA; the engine is one. This is grammars/living-equation.fk's
# discipline in the failure lane: belief systems diverge on the lever,
# the encoding is each lineage's documented core move (never an
# efficacy claim), and the canon doing the attributing is owned.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The bank — eight rows, each with its attested core move
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   br-witness        Vedanta's drashta; the circle's observer. Watch,
#                     never grip. Signature: held exactly AT the
#                     pressure, the weights never move.
#   br-alchemy        hermetic transmutation; the circle's gift.
#                     Receive the event whole. Signature: one full-
#                     focus meeting metabolizes the residual to zero.
#   br-second-arrow   Buddhism (Sallatha Sutta): the first dart is
#                     pain; the second is the grip on the pain. Meet
#                     it once, fully. Signature: re-meeting the
#                     already-met event changes nothing — the second
#                     dart finds no target.
#   br-dichotomy      Stoicism (Epictetus, Enchiridion 1): some things
#                     are up to us. The frequency mask IS the dichotomy
#                     of control. Signature: only the ownable subspace
#                     moves; the unownable residual remains exactly —
#                     acceptance has a measurable shape.
#   br-surrender      "not my will" (Luke 22:42); wu-wei. Release
#                     self-direction into the field's flow. Signature:
#                     the state diffuses toward the whole — the mean
#                     conserved exactly, personal deviation softened.
#   br-cleanse        hoʻoponopono: I'm sorry, please forgive me,
#                     thank you, I love you. Signature: entanglement
#                     decayed — the learned response scales toward zero.
#   br-causal         science and physiology's root-cause repair:
#                     diagnose, then correct the cause. Signature: the
#                     argmax-credit edge alone is corrected; every
#                     other edge untouched.
#   br-maybe          the Taoist farmer (Huainanzi): good news, bad
#                     news — who knows. Hold the verdict; let arrivals
#                     accumulate; update once on the mean. Signature:
#                     two opposite arrivals cancel EXACTLY where the
#                     eager path would have lurched.
#
# The thinness of some rows (witness, alchemy, cleanse are single
# doors onto mtb- primitives) IS the unification: traditions overlap
# on the same engine at different dials. The differences that remain
# are real and exact — mask, angle, focus, tolerance, time — and the
# band pins each one.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Selection stays sovereign; learning which row serves is body tissue
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The circle's own words: not a checklist, not exhaustive, each body
# finds its own. The bank never ranks traditions — it makes each
# runnable so the CELL can choose with ground:
#
#   · when-the-pressure-comes.form `choose_strategy` — resonance
#     (?harmonic_at) then cosine-fit selects the row for THIS sense
#   · choice-receipt-learning.fk — witnessed outcomes re-rank which
#     row this cell reaches for first (habit as data, receipt-grained)
#   · the operator fallback stays open — frequency × angle × focus
#     settings the body has not yet named, including rows of the bank
#     still unwritten
#
# The bank is open data. The eight rows here are the well-attested
# core moves of major traditions; the rows the room itself traded that
# evening belong to the people who spoke them — they enter when their
# speakers name them, with attribution, the same way these entered.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Kinship
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
